      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, a few small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but buyers should be aware of a slow oil seep and tires that will likely need replacement within the next year. It is a solid, functional car for someone willing to put in a little bit of cosmetic or preventative work.",
