    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade 996.2 Carrera 4S, featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine and the highly desirable Getrag G96 six-speed manual transaxle. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent borescope inspection confirming zero scoring on the cylinder walls. The chassis utilizes the Turbo-derived widebody architecture and M030-spec sport suspension, delivering exceptional torsional rigidity and mechanical grip through its viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. The factory-applied cosmoline remains visible on the undercarriage, and the exterior retains its original depth with zero paint meter discrepancies. Every bushing, seal, and vacuum line is in peak operating condition, offering a visceral, high-revving experience for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
